          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2060.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a separate baking tray with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p>\n<p>Unwrap the <strong>puff pastry </strong>and cut it into 2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4]</span> squares </p>\n<p>Score a 1cm border around the edge of the pastry with a knife</p>\n<p>Crimp the borders with a fork and put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until puffed up and golden – these are your <strong>pie lids</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
